Package com.st.st25sdk Description

The ST25SDK provides a rich and well tested Software Development Kit for the ST25 tags and Dynamics tags. ST25SDK provides several API levels from high level features such as Tags or NDEF to lowest level with NFC and ISO commands including also ST25 portfolio custom features.
